      <title>南非财政部因水务债务暂停市政资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/south-africa-treasury-to-suspend-municipal-funds-over-water-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非财政部计划下个月扣留五个市政府的资金，以补偿它们拖欠的水费，这是迫使地方政府支付基本服务费用的举措之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/south-africa-treasury-to-suspend-municipal-funds-over-water-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 14:07:12 GMT</pubDate>
